title: The Accidental Prime Minister
subTitle: Amidst the political upheaval, Dr Manmohan Singh, an Indian economist, faces several challenges during his tenure as the Prime Minister of India.

title: Holiday
subTitle: Muskaan, an unpopular, shy girl, falls for Dino, a charismatic dancer, while on a vacation in Goa with her family. However, things become complicated when her father objects to their relationship.

title: Qarib Qarib Singlle
subTitle: Jaya and Yogi, two contrasting personalities, set out to retrace past relationships, sparking the most eventful trip of their lives.

title: India Lockdown
subTitle: The lives of four individuals - a father, his pilot daughter, a prostitute, and a migrant worker - are thrown into turmoil when the Indian government announces a nationwide lockdown.

title: Daddy
subTitle: Arun Gawli rises from poverty and becomes one of India's most notable gangsters. However, hungry for more power and influence, he launches a career in politics.

title: Phobia
subTitle: A woman becomes agoraphobic after being assaulted by a taxi driver. She becomes convinced that a malevolent force has taken over the very home in which she is trapped.

title: Veere Di Wedding
subTitle: Four young women navigate love, family, and careers while supporting one another. The childhood friends are brought together for Kalindi's wedding and are forced to untangle their lives.

title: Sam Bahadur
subTitle: Sam Manekshaw, an Indian army officer, navigates through his eventful life filled with ups and downs, including him getting promoted to the rank of Field Marshal.

title: Manmarziyaan
subTitle: A young, free-spirited woman is torn between two very different men and must decide who to marry. One is an immature, part-time DJ, while the other is a mature and responsible banker.

title: Toofaan
subTitle: Aziz Ali, an orphan who works for a thug, meets Ananya, who encourages him to pursue his passion for boxing. However, one wrong decision costs him his career.

title: Bawaal
subTitle: A small-town man falls in love with the prettiest girl in town. However, he ends up marrying her in order to raise his social standing.

title: The Tashkent Files
subTitle: Following the mysterious death of India's second prime minister, Lal Bahadur Shastri, a team launches a probe into the conspiracy of it being an assassination.

title: Waah Zindagi
subTitle: A struggling farmer's son sets out to become an entrepreneur and win over his childhood love. However, foreign businesses threaten to ruin his path to success.

title: Chakravyuh
subTitle: Kabir infiltrates a Maoist organisation to help Adil Khan, who is a decorated police officer and his friend. As he gets deeper into the organisation, Kabir starts sympathising with the group's plight and starts having second thoughts.

title: Madaari
subTitle: Nirmal, a man who lost his son due to the negligence of the government, seeks revenge and kidnaps the ten-year-old son of the home minister, forcing the administration to meet his demands.

title: Sherdil: The Pilibhit Saga
subTitle: A sacrificed village leader, Gangaram, embarks on a journey in search of a dangerous tiger that threatens people.

title: Love Hostel
subTitle: A series of bloodshed, escapes and deception ensue when Jyothi and Ashu elope together and her family hires a ruthless mercenary to kill the couple.

title: Thappad
subTitle: Amrita, a young woman, leads a content life with her husband, Vikram. However, their happiness is shattered when he slaps her at an office party, causing her to file for a divorce.

title: Trapped
subTitle: A desperate Shaurya moves into an empty high-rise building where he and his lover can stay. However, things take a dark turn when he finds himself locked in his new apartment without any amenities.

title: Auron Mein Kahan Dum Tha
subTitle: As Krishna, an incarcerated man, faces early release, his love story with Vasudha from more than twenty years ago unfurls.

title: Hamari Adhuri Kahani
subTitle: Half a decade after her husband went missing, Vasudha, a single mother, falls for Aarav, a hotelier. However, her missing husband, Hari, returns, thereby creating a rift between the two lovers.

title: The Sabarmati Report
subTitle: Years after the Sabarmati Express tragedy, Samar Kumar teams up with a novice journalist when the latter stumbles upon a suppressed report, leading to a dangerous quest for the truth.

title: Hotel Mumbai
subTitle: A hotel staff risks everything to keep its patrons safe during a terror attack, especially a British heiress, her husband and her infant.
